PalmJob Job Character Image Prompt (Template)

ROLE / GOAL
- Create a single square (1:1) hero image for PalmJob, a playful palm-reading job recommendation service.
- The image must visually represent the unique job title: "{{JOB_TITLE}}".
- The image is used as a result card illustration, so it should be clean, readable, and consistent across different jobs.

STYLE REFERENCE
- Art direction: Pixar / Disney / Dreamworks animation style
- 3D render quality: Nintendo Switch game cutscene or high-end mobile game character
- NOT hyperrealistic, NOT anime, NOT flat 2D illustration
- Warm, inviting, universally appealing aesthetic

SUBJECT (MAIN)
- One friendly, whimsical 3D {{GENDER}} character (single subject only).
- The character clearly embodies the essence of "{{JOB_TITLE}}" via outfit, props, posture, and small symbolic details.
- Interpret the job creatively (it can be slightly fantastical), but keep the design universally appealing.
- The character should feel like they genuinely love their job.

CHARACTER DESIGN
- **Gender**: {{GENDER}} character - design should clearly reflect this while maintaining the stylized, approachable aesthetic
- **Face & Expression**: Big expressive eyes, warm genuine smile, friendly and approachable vibe
- **Body Type**: Stylized proportions (slightly large head, compact body), NOT realistic human proportions
- **Skin/Appearance**: Diverse representation welcome (vary skin tones, features), but keep stylized/illustrated look
- **Material**: Smooth, soft-beveled surfaces like a high-quality vinyl toy or Funko Pop figure

OUTFIT & PROPS GUIDE
- **Outfit**: Simplified, stylized uniform/costume that hints at "{{JOB_TITLE}}"
  - Use color coding and iconic silhouettes rather than hyper-detailed textures
  - Avoid real-world brand logos or copyrighted designs
- **Props**: 1~3 iconic tools/objects that symbolize "{{JOB_TITLE}}"
  - Props should be easily recognizable even at thumbnail size
  - Floating or held naturally by the character

### Job Category Hints (for props/outfit inspiration)
- **미래/기술 직업**: 홀로그램, 로봇 부품, VR 고글, 우주복 요소, 디지털 파티클
- **감성/치유 직업**: 하트, 부드러운 빛, 따뜻한 색상의 오브젝트, 포옹 제스처
- **자연/환경 직업**: 나뭇잎, 별, 구름, 무지개, 자연 요소들
- **창의/예술 직업**: 붓, 팔레트, 음표, 빛줄기, 추상적 형태
- **꿈/신비 직업**: 달, 별, 안개, 수정구, 몽환적 파티클
- **시간/기억 직업**: 시계, 모래시계, 빛나는 조각들, 필름 프레임
- **행운/일상 직업**: 클로버, 주사위, 별똥별, 반짝이는 오브젝트

SCENE / BACKGROUND
- **Background Style**: Dreamy, soft gradient using PalmJob brand colors
- **Brand Color Palette**:
  - Primary: Purple #7C3AED (main gradient color)
  - Accent: Pink #EC4899 (gradient blend)
  - Highlight: Amber #F59E0B (very subtle sparkle accents only)
- **Gradient Direction**: Top-left to bottom-right, smooth transition
- **Decorative Elements**:
  - Subtle "palm line" pattern overlay (very low opacity, background only)
  - Soft sparkles / light particles (magical feeling, not cluttered)
  - Optional: Gentle glow behind character for depth

COMPOSITION
- **Framing**: Centered subject, symmetrical composition
- **Safe Margins**: Generous padding (do not crop the character)
- **Silhouette Clarity**: Job-defining props must be readable at thumbnail size (< 200px)
- **Depth**: Character slightly in front of background elements
- **Text**: Absolutely NO text elements anywhere in the image

CAMERA / RENDER
- **Camera Angle**: Slightly below eye level, looking up at character (heroic feel)
- **Lens**: Standard focal length, no distortion
- **Render Style**: 
  - Studio-quality 3D render
  - Global illumination with soft shadows
  - Octane Render / Unreal Engine 5 / Cinema 4D quality
- **Lighting Setup**:
  - Key light: Soft, warm, from upper-left (45°)
  - Fill light: Cool purple tint, from right side
  - Rim light: Gentle edge highlight for depth separation
  - Ambient occlusion: Mild, for grounding
- **Post-processing**: 
  - Subtle bloom on bright areas
  - No heavy film grain
  - Crisp but not harsh

TECHNICAL SPECS
- Resolution: 1024x1024 pixels
- Aspect Ratio: 1:1 (Square)
- Output: Clean, social-card ready
- Quality Keywords: photorealistic 3D render, octane render, unreal engine 5, ray tracing, volumetric lighting, 8K quality

NEGATIVE CONSTRAINTS (MUST NOT INCLUDE)
- ❌ No text, letters, numbers, captions, signatures, watermarks, or logos
- ❌ No UI elements, frames, borders, or mockups
- ❌ No copyrighted / recognizable characters (Mickey Mouse, Mario, etc.)
- ❌ No extra characters, no crowds, no duplicated limbs or artifacts
- ❌ No background clutter; keep it simple and clean
- ❌ No realistic human photos or hyperrealistic renders
- ❌ No dark, scary, or negative imagery
- ❌ No weapons, violence, or inappropriate content

